- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper focuses on modeling uplink transmission in cellular wireless networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses power control policies for interference mitigation and robust uplink communication, which are related to control systems. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper does not explicitly deal with multimedia, but it may be relevant in the context of wireless multimedia transmission in cellular networks. 
- cs.PF (Performance): The paper analyzes the performance of uplink transmission in cellular networks, which is related to performance evaluation and optimization.
